RESERVATIONS
Reservations may be made at any office of TWA or other airline-but
reservations must be made in advance.
Space cannot be definitely held until
tickets are actually arranged for; tickets must be purchased at least three hours
before scheduled departure time on any flight departing between the hours of
10:01 A.M. and 12:00 midnight or by 9:00 P.M. on the day prior to departure
on any flight scheduled to depart between the hours of 12:01 A.M. and 10:00 A.M.
Transcontinental and Western Air, Inc., reserves the right to cancel any reser-
vation, or refuse to carry any person when such action is necessary to accommodate
persons traveling on missions relating to the successful prosecution of the war,
or when, in the opinion of Transcontinental and Western Air, Inc., such action is
necessary for any other reason relating to the successful prosecution of the war.
